'''基蘭·蒂爾尼'''（{{lang-en|Kieran Tierney}}；{{bd|1997年|6月5日}}），是一名[[蘇格蘭|蘇格蘭]]職業足球員，現時效力[[英格蘭超級足球聯賽|英格蘭超級足球聯賽]]球隊[[阿仙奴足球會|阿仙奴]]和[[蘇格蘭足球代表隊|蘇格蘭足球代表隊]]<ref name="soccerway">{{cite web|url=https://www.skysports.com/football/news/11065/11779719/kieran-tierney-fee-agreed-between-arsenal-and-celtic/|title=Scotland - K. Tierney - Profile with news, career statistics and history - Soccerway|publisher=soccerway.com|accessdate=2015-04-23|language=en|archive-date=2019-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190808021700/https://www.skysports.com/football/news/11065/11779719/kieran-tierney-fee-agreed-between-arsenal-and-celtic|dead-url=no}}</ref>。司職[[左閘|左閘]]。

蒂爾尼為些路迪的青訓球員，於2015年4月首次為球隊上陣，1年後首次為蘇格蘭足球代表隊上陣。2019年8月，他以2500萬鎊的價錢轉投阿仙奴，成為最高轉會費的蘇格蘭球員。<ref name="兵工廠"/>

== 球會生涯 ==
=== 早期生涯 ===
蒂爾尼於[[曼島|-{zh-hans:马恩岛;zh-hk:萌島;zh-tw:曼島;}-]]的[[道格拉斯_(马恩岛)|道格拉斯]]出生<ref name="iom"/>，於10個月大時移居至[[威蕭|威蕭]]<ref name=gemmell>{{cite news|url=http://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/news/local-news/wishaws-kieran-tierney-pays-tribute-10030469|title=Wishaw's Kieran Tierney pays tribute to Celtic legend Tommy Gemmell|last=Temlett|first=Michael|date=2017-03-18|work=Daily Record|publisher=Trinity Mirror|language=en|accessdate=2017-05-02|archive-date=2017-04-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170419044859/http://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/news/local-news/wishaws-kieran-tierney-pays-tribute-10030469|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他小時候支持的球隊為[[凱爾特人足球俱樂部|些路迪]]，並於7歲時加入球隊的青年隊。蒂爾尼曾表示希望模仿[[里斯本雄狮|里斯本雄狮]]的成員{{link-en|托米·格梅爾|Tommy Gemmell}}，因為二人皆於[[威蕭|威蕭]]成長，並出任相同的位置<ref name=gemmell/>。

蒂爾尼為球隊各階的青年軍上陣，並成為青年隊邊路中攻守皆能的球員<ref name="debut">{{cite web|last=McKay|first=Kenny|title=Kieran Tierney determined to make further progress at the club|url=http://www.celticfc.net/news/6395|website=Celtic FC|accessdate=2015-08-02|date=2014-08-06|language=en|archive-date=2014-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140806225108/http://www.celticfc.net/news/6395|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。2014年8月，他跟隨一線隊出戰對陣[[托定咸熱刺足球會|托定咸熱刺]]的友誼賽，並在比賽中得到出場機會。雖然些路迪在比賽中落敗，但蒂爾尼仍形容他的一線隊首戰為「夢想成真」<ref name="debut" />。2014-15賽季，他繼續為些路迪的預備隊上陣。2014年10月，蒂爾尼在對陣[[哈茨足球俱乐部|赫斯]]的青年軍比賽中，於自己禁區頂的位置施射，攻入1球<ref>{{cite web|last1=McKay|first1=Kenny|title=Kieran Tierney wonder goal secures Celtic win|url=http://www.celticfc.net/news/6964|website=Celtic FC|accessdate=2015-08-02|language=en|date=2014-10-28|archive-date=2015-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923221701/http://www.celticfc.net/news/6964|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Kyle|first1=Gregor|title=Video: Celtic kid Kieran Tierney scores from edge of his own penalty box|url=http://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/video-celtic-kid-kieran-tierney-4533534|website=Daily Record|accessdate=2015-08-02|date=2014-10-30|language=en|archive-date=2014-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141030200258/http://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/video-celtic-kid-kieran-tierney-4533534|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 些路迪 ===
==== 一線隊首戰與突破 ====
2015年4月22日，蒂爾尼於正式比賽中首次為些路迪上陣。領隊{{link-en|羅尼·代拉|Ronny Deila}}於聯賽對陣[[邓迪足球俱乐部|登地]]的比賽中，於第81分鐘派遣他上陣<ref name="soccerway2">{{cite web|url=http://int.soccerway.com/matches/2015/04/22/scotland/premier-league/dundee-fc/celtic-fc/1704591/|title=Dundee vs. Celtic — Soccerway|publisher=soccerway.com|accessdate=2015-04-23|language=en|archive-date=2015-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150422211701/http://int.soccerway.com/matches/2015/04/22/scotland/premier-league/dundee-fc/celtic-fc/1704591/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該季，他在對陣[[圣庄士东足球俱乐部|聖莊士東]]的比賽中，再為球隊上陣，該場比賽中，他上陣超過60分鐘<ref>{{cite web|title=Games Involving Tierney, Kieran In Season 2014/2015|url=http://www.fitbastats.com/celtic/player_games.php?playerid=6774&page=2|website=FitbaStats|accessdate=2015-08-02|language=en|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924043302/http://www.fitbastats.com/celtic/player_games.php?playerid=6774&page=2|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

2015-16賽季，蒂爾尼為球隊上陣超過30場比賽，取代[[埃米利奥·伊扎古雷|-{zh-hans:伊扎古雷;zh-hk:伊薩古利;zh-hant:伊扎古雷}-]]，成為球隊的正選[[左閘|左閘]]<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.heraldscotland.com/news/14314216.Tierney__I_took_Emilio_s_Celtic_place_but_he_still_helps_me_every_day/|title=Kieran Tierney: I took Emilio Izaguirre's Celtic place but he still helps me every day|last=Macpherson|first=Graeme|date=2016-03-02|work=The Herald|publisher=Newsquest|accessdate=2016-10-17|archive-date=2016-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161018224621/http://www.heraldscotland.com/news/14314216.Tierney__I_took_Emilio_s_Celtic_place_but_he_still_helps_me_every_day/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。蒂爾尼出色的表現助他獲得[[蘇格蘭PFA年度最佳青年球員|蘇格蘭PFA年度最佳青年球員]]和[[蘇格蘭FWA年度最佳青年球員|蘇格蘭FWA年度最佳青年球員]]的獎項，些路迪在該季亦獲得聯賽冠軍<ref name = "players 2016"/><ref name = "writers 2016"/>。雖然有部份[[英格蘭超級足球聯賽|英格蘭超級足球聯賽]]球隊有意收購他，蒂爾尼仍選擇於2016年6月24日與球會續約，新合約年期直至2021年完結<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/36620462|title=Celtic: Kieran Tierney signs five-year contract extension|last=Barnes|first=John|date=2016-06-24|work=BBC Sport|accessdate=2017-03-10|language=en|archive-date=2017-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170407031134/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/36620462|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==== 2016-17賽季 ====
於[[2016–17年歐洲冠軍聯賽分組賽|2016–17年歐洲冠軍聯賽分組賽]]首次上陣後，蒂爾尼在10月27日於訓練中弄傷[[腳踝|腳踝]]韌帶，需最少缺陣2個月，將錯過聯賽盃決賽<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/37797772|title=Kieran Tierney: Celtic and Scotland defender ruled out for two months|date=29 October 2016|publisher=BBC Sport|accessdate=30 October 2016|archive-date=2017-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170321164357/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/37797772|dead-url=no}}</ref>。於缺陣期間，他同時醫治反復出現的肩膀傷患，亦在朋友陪同下，以支持者的身份入場觀看數場些路迪的比賽<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/sport/football/scottish/celtic/injured-tierney-savoured-roaring-on-celts-in-stands-35422285.html|title=Injured Tierney savoured roaring on Celts in stands|date=2017-02-04|language=en|publisher=Belfast Telegraph|accessdate=2017-11-08|archive-date=2017-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171109023324/https://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/sport/football/scottish/celtic/injured-tierney-savoured-roaring-on-celts-in-stands-35422285.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-4249740/amp/Celtic-defender-Kieran-Tierney-loved-injury-layoff.html|title=Celtic defender Kieran Tierney 'loved' injury layoff after watching his team-mates from the Parkhead stands|date= 2017-02-22|publisher=Daily Mail|accessdate= 2017-11-08|language= en}}</ref>。

2017年1月22日，蒂爾尼在缺陣3個月後，在[[蘇格蘭足總盃|蘇格蘭足總盃]]對陣[[阿爾比恩流浪者足球會|阿爾比恩流浪者]]的比賽中復出<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/38626880|title=Albion Rovers 0–3 Celtic|last=Wilson|first=Richard|date=2017-01-22|publisher=BBC Sport|accessdate=2017-05-08|language=en|archive-date=2017-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170220223739/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/38626880|dead-url=no}}</ref>。5月7日，他再次獲得[[蘇格蘭PFA年度最佳青年球員|蘇格蘭PFA年度最佳青年球員]]的獎項，是繼{{link-en|奇治·尼雲|Craig Levein}}贏得1984-85賽季和1985-86賽季的獎項後，首位連續贏得此獎項的球員<ref name = "pfa 2017">{{cite news|url=https://stv.tv/sport/football/1387806-celtic-seal-a-treble-of-awards-at-pfa-scotland-ceremony/|title=Celtic seal a treble of awards at PFA Scotland ceremony|last=Brannan|first=Laura|date=2017-05-07|publisher=stv.tv|accessdate=2017-05-08|language=en|archive-date=2017-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170929000735/https://stv.tv/sport/football/1387806-celtic-seal-a-treble-of-awards-at-pfa-scotland-ceremony/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2017年蘇格蘭足總盃決賽中，他的下顎受傷，被提早換下接受治療，些路迪最終以2比1贏得比賽，成為國內[[三冠王|三冠王]]，其中聯賽更以不敗奪冠<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/football/2017/05/27/celtic-2-aberdeen-1tom-rogic-shatters-dons-secure-historic-clean/ | title=Celtic 2 Aberdeen 1: Tom Rogic shatters Dons to secure historic clean sweep with Scottish Cup final win | publisher=The Daily Telegraph | date=2017-05-27 | language=en | accessdate=2017-05-30 | archive-date=2017-05-28 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170528113842/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/football/2017/05/27/celtic-2-aberdeen-1tom-rogic-shatters-dons-secure-historic-clean/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。雖然蒂爾尼於本賽季受傷時間比較長，他仍能為球隊上陣40場比賽。

==== 2017-18賽季 ====
2017年8月8日，蒂爾尼在[[蘇格蘭聯賽盃|蘇格蘭聯賽盃]]對陣[[基马诺克足球俱乐部|基马诺克]]的比賽中成為球隊的隊長，並出任中堅的位置，帶領陣中其他的年輕球員。在比賽中，他交出1次助攻，並於40碼外射入1球，協助球隊以5比0大勝<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/40829930 |title=Celtic 5–0 Kilmarnock |publisher=BBC Sport |date=2017-08-08 |language=en |accessdate=2017-08-08 |archive-date=2017-08-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170811153657/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/40829930 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。10月30日，於贏得聯賽最大對手[[阿伯丁足球俱乐部|鴨巴甸]]的比賽後一星期，他與球會續下1份年期至2023年的合約<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/41810466|title=Kieran Tierney: Celtic left-back signs new six-year contract|date=2017-02-22|language=en|publisher=BBC Sport|accessdate=2017-11-08|archive-date=2017-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171107143845/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/41810466|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==== 2018-19賽季 ====
2018年12月2日，蒂爾尼於{{link-en|2018年蘇格蘭足總盃決賽|2018 Scottish League Cup Final}}中上陣全場的比賽<ref name=lc1819/>，其後因髋部受傷，至次年2月24日才復出<ref>{{cite web|title=Celtic star Kieran Tierney blasts Motherwell over lack of respect after sneaky throw-in goal|url=https://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/celtic-star-kieran-tierney-blasts-14048209|publisher=|work=Daily Record|date=2019-02-24|language=en|accessdate=2019-02-25|archive-date=2019-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190225045215/https://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/celtic-star-kieran-tierney-blasts-14048209|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他在餘下的賽季，因[[疝氣|疝氣]]而需接受手術<ref name="hernia">{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/48731196|title=Kieran Tierney: Arsenal 'optimistic' over Celtic defender deal|last=Ornstein|first=David|date=2019-06-22|work=|publisher=BBC Sport|accessdate=2019-06-22|language=en|archive-date=2019-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190622170507/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/48731196|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 阿仙奴===
2019年8月8日，蒂爾尼轉會[[英格蘭超級足球聯賽|英格蘭超級足球聯賽]]球隊[[阿仙奴足球會|阿仙奴]]，轉會費據報為2500萬鎊<ref>{{Cite web|url= https://www.arsenal.com/news/kieran-tierney-joins-long-term-deal|title= Kieran Tierney joins on long-term deal|website= Arsenal.com|language= en|access-date= 2019-08-08|date= 2019-08-08|archive-date= 2019-08-08|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190808155104/https://www.arsenal.com/news/kieran-tierney-joins-long-term-deal|dead-url= no}}</ref><ref name="兵工廠">{{cite web |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/49283667 |title=Kieran Tierney: Celtic defender completes £25m Arsenal move |work= |publisher=BBC Sport |date=2019-08-08 |accessdate=2019-08-08 |language=en |archive-date=2019-08-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190808170510/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/49283667 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他因接受疝氣手術而缺陣季初的賽事<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/49780536 |title=Kieran Tierney: Scotland defender makes injury comeback for Arsenal U23 |website=BBC Sport |date=2019-09-21 |language=en |accessdate=2019-09-21 |archive-date=2019-09-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190921090511/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/49780536 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。9月24日，蒂爾尼於[[英格蘭聯賽盃|英格蘭聯賽盃]]對陣[[诺丁汉森林足球俱乐部|诺丁汉森林]]的比賽中，首次代表球隊上陣<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/49823156 |title=Kieran Tierney: Scotland full-back enjoys impressive Arsenal debut |website=BBC Sport |date=2019-09-25 |accessdate=2019-09-25 |language=en |archive-date=2019-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190925093458/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/49823156 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。一星期後，他於[[欧足联欧洲联赛|欧足联欧洲联赛]]主勝[[皇家標準列治|標準列治]]4比0的比賽中，交出助攻予[[加布里埃爾·馬丁內利|-{zh-hans:加布里埃尔·马蒂内利;zh-hk:加比爾·馬天尼利;zh-tw:加布里埃爾·馬丁內利;}-]]<ref>{{cite web |url= https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/49874359 |title= Arsenal 4–0 Standard Liege |website= BBC Sport |date= 2019-10-03 |accessdate= 2019-10-08 |language= en |archive-date= 2019-10-03 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20191003043401/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/49874359 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。10月27日，蒂爾尼於對陣[[水晶宫足球俱乐部|水晶宫]]的比賽中，首次於英超上陣，雙方最終以2比2賽和<ref>{{Cite web|url= https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/50113576|title= Arsenal 2–2 Crystal Palace: Gunners surrender two-goal advantage as Granit Xhaka booed off|date= 2019-10-27|language= en|website= BBC|accessdate= 2020-07-18|archive-date= 2019-10-26|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20191026012508/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/50113576|dead-url= no}}</ref>。他於對陣[[韋斯咸足球會|韋斯咸]]的聯賽中，因肩膀脫臼缺陣一段時間。

聯賽因[[2019冠状病毒病疫情|2019冠状病毒病疫情]]緩和而復賽後，蒂爾尼於6月有着好表現，獲得該月球會最佳球員的獎項<ref>{{Cite web|url= https://www.arsenal.com/news/tierney-our-june-player-month|title= Tierney is our June Player of the Month!|date= 2020-07-13|accessdate= 2020-07-13|language= en|website= BBC|archive-date= 2020-07-13|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200713150320/https://www.arsenal.com/news/tierney-our-june-player-month|dead-url= no}}</ref>。2020年7月26日，蒂爾尼於聯賽煞科戰對陣[[屈福特足球會|屈福特]]的比賽中，攻入轉會後首個入球，協助球隊於主場以3比2勝出<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/kieran-tierney-mark-arsenal-former-22419340 |title=Kieran Tierney off the mark for Arsenal as former Celtic star scores first Premier League goal |first=Steven |last=Mair |newspaper=Daily Record |publisher= |date=2020-07-26 |accessdate=2020-07-26 |language=en |archive-date=2020-07-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200726161927/https://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/kieran-tierney-mark-arsenal-former-22419340 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。8月1日，蒂爾尼以正選上陣{{link-en|2020年英格蘭足總盃決賽|2020 FA Cup Final}}，助球隊贏得第14次冠軍<ref name="bbc">{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/53546100 |title=Arsenal 2–1 Chelsea |first=Phil |last=McNulty |website=BBC Sport |date=2020-08-01 |language=en |accessdate=2020-08-02 |archive-date=2020-08-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200801202716/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/53546100 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2021年2月25日，蒂爾尼在[[歐足總歐洲聯賽|歐足總歐洲聯賽]]32強賽中以3-2擊敗[[里斯本與本菲卡體育|本菲卡]]的比賽踢進一球，因此他成為自1980年3月{{link-en|威利·楊|Willie Young (footballer, born 1951)}}以來在歐戰中首位為阿森納進球的蘇格蘭人。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/56185885 |title=Arsenal 3–2 Benfica |website=BBC Sport |date=2021-02-25 |language=en |access-date=2021-02-26 |archive-date=2021-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227120221/https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/56185885 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2021年6月25日，蒂爾尼與阿仙奴簽下續約，新合約到2026年<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.arsenal.com/news/here-stay-tierney-signs-long-term-deal |title=Here to stay! Tierney signs long-term deal |website=arsenal.com |date=2021-06-26 |language=en |access-date=2021-06-26 |archive-date=2021-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210706163158/https://www.arsenal.com/news/here-stay-tierney-signs-long-term-deal |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 國家隊生涯 ==
蒂爾尼曾為{{link-en|蘇格蘭18歲以下足球代表隊|Scotland national football team|蘇格蘭 U18}}和{{link-en|蘇格蘭19歲以下足球代表隊|Scotland national under-19 football team|蘇格蘭 U19}}上陣<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.scottishfa.co.uk/football_player_profile.cfm?page=1848&playerID=141507&squadID=9 |title=Kieran Tierney |work=www.scottishfa.co.uk |publisher=Scottish Football Association |date= |accessdate=2015-10-03 |language=en |archive-date=2015-10-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151004012558/http://www.scottishfa.co.uk/football_player_profile.cfm?page=1848&playerID=141507&squadID=9 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，他亦曾表示有興趣為出生地的國家隊——{{link-en|曼島足球代表隊|Ellan Vannin football team}}上陣<ref name=iom/>。

2016年3月10日，蒂爾尼於對陣[[丹麥國家足球隊|丹麥國家足球隊]]的友誼賽，首次獲[[蘇格蘭足球代表隊|蘇格蘭足球代表隊]]徵召<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/35770855|title=Scotland: Six new call-ups for Czech Republic and Denmark friendlies|date=2016-03-10|work=BBC Sport|publisher=BBC|accessdate=2016-03-10|language=en|archive-date=2016-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310175550/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/35770855|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並在比賽中上陣45分鐘，於下半場開始時被些路迪隊友[[查理·穆爾格魯|查理·穆爾格魯]]入替，最終蘇格蘭隊於主場[[咸普頓公園球場|咸普頓公園球場]]以1比0勝出<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/35923550 |title=Scotland 1–0 Denmark: McGinn and Tierney shine on debuts |first=Alasdair |last=Lamont |work=BBC Sport |publisher=BBC |date=2016-03-30 |accessdate=2016-04-06 |language=en |archive-date=2016-04-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160405045401/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/35923550 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

由於國家隊隊友[[安祖·羅拔臣|-{zh-hans:安德鲁·罗伯逊;zh-hk:安祖·羅拔臣;}-]]於左閘的位置有着出色的表現<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/andrew-robertson-stuart-armstrong-drive-10587690 |title=Andrew Robertson and Stuart Armstrong have the drive and hunger to be Scotland stars for years — Jackie McNamara |publisher=Daily Record |date=2017-06-09 |accessdate=2017-08-08 |language=en |archive-date=2017-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170809041756/http://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/andrew-robertson-stuart-armstrong-drive-10587690 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，加上蒂爾尼能出任多個防守位置，因此他在對陣[[斯洛文尼亞國家足球隊|斯洛文尼亞國家足球隊]]、[[立陶宛國家足球隊|立陶宛國家足球隊]]和[[斯洛伐克國家足球隊|斯洛伐克國家足球隊]]的比賽中出任右閘<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/39302192 |title=Scotland 1–0 Slovenia |publisher=BBC Sport |date=2017-03-26 |accessdate=2017-08-09 |language=en |archive-date=2017-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170823190011/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/39302192 |dead-url=no }}</ref>；而在[[2018年國際足協世界盃外圍賽_–_歐洲區F組|2018年國際足協世界盃外圍賽]]對陣[[英格蘭國家足球隊|英格蘭國家足球隊]]的比賽中，他出任[[中堅|左中堅]]的位置<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/blog/2017/jun/11/scotland-england-five-talking-points-tierney-strachan-sterling-oxlade-chamberlain |title=Scotland 2–2 England |publisher=The Guardian |date=2017-06-11 |accessdate=2017-08-09 |language=en |archive-date=2017-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170809041705/https://www.theguardian.com/football/blog/2017/jun/11/scotland-england-five-talking-points-tierney-strachan-sterling-oxlade-chamberlain |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2017年11月10日，蒂爾尼在對陣[[荷蘭國家足球隊|荷蘭國家足球隊]]的比賽中首次成為球隊的隊長，並出任中堅，但球隊最終以0比1落敗<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/41840573 |title=Scotland 0—1 Netherlands |work=The Scotsman |date=2017-11-09 |language=en |accessdate=2017-11-10 |archive-date=2017-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171109234209/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/41840573 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2022年3月24日，蒂爾尼在對陣[[波蘭国家足球队|波蘭]]的友誼賽中踢進在[[蘇格蘭足球代表隊|蘇格蘭足球代表隊]]的首球<ref>{{cite web|title=Scotland 1-1 Poland: Krzysztof Piatek rules out Kieran Tierney's first international goal|url=https://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-10649799/Scotland-1-1-Poland-Krzysztof-Pi-tek-rules-Kieran-Tierney-international-goal.html|publisher=Daily Mail|date=2022-03-24|access-date=2022-03-25|archive-date=2022-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220415180815/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-10649799/Scotland-1-1-Poland-Krzysztof-Pi-tek-rules-Kieran-Tierney-international-goal.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

